# Contact-form delivery (Web3Forms — https://web3forms.com)
# Get a free access key by entering your email on their homepage (no account).
# The key is spam-protected and safe to expose in client code.
# Copy this file to `.env`, paste your key, and add the same var to the Vercel
# project's Environment Variables so it's set on the deployed build too.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
